==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Livonian
<hw>Li*vo"ni*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to Livonia, a district on the Baltic Sea formerly part of Russia, now
part of Latvia and Estonia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Livonian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Livonian
<hw>Li*vo"ni*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or an inhabitant of
Livonia; the language (allied to the Finnish) of the
Livonians.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Livor</ent>⟦br⟧
